David Faustino https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Faustino 0 David Anthony Faustino (born March 3, 1974) is an American actor and rapper primarily known for his role as Bud Bundy on the FOX sitcom Married... with Children. David Faustino is currently the host of Old Scratch Radio Sundays on Skee 24/7 on Dash Radio.
